  "title": "Fleet Operations Supervisor (1-year Contract)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our client is a local leading player in FMCG industry.</strong><br /><br />Location: West (walking distance from MRT)<br />Salary: Up to $2,800 + Allowance + completion bonus<br />Working Hours: 5 days work week (including weekends)<br />Duration: 12 Months</p><p>Duties of Fleet Operations Supervisor:</p><ul><li>Plan and optimize efficient B2B delivery routes using transportation management systems.</li><li>Oversee daily delivery operations to ensure timely, accurate service and resolve any issues.</li><li>Manage and support drivers on routes, procedures, documentation, and safety protocols.</li><li>Ensure compliance with safety regulations and vehicle maintenance standards.</li><li>Monitor KPIs to improve delivery performance, route efficiency, and overall operations</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>At least 2 years of experience in fleet management and delivery route planning</li><li>Comfortable with 5 days rotating day shifts</li><li>Possess supervisory experience </li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click <strong>APPLY NOW</strong> or email an updated copy of your resume / cv.</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p><ul><li><strong>Email Address: jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></li><li>Recruitpedia Pte. Ltd.</li><li>EA License No. 19C9682</li><li>EA Reg. No. R22108850 (Chan Mun Mun)</li></ul>",
